title: DAZ3D - CityScapes Backdrops Volume 2
description:
---Previously uploaded to KAT by ArgosDaz---

CityScapes Backdrops Volume 2 contains 8 additional beautifully alpha mapped city lines to add to your collection. These are 2D Backdrops which are very useful when you need a quick background, window view or to create a great depth of field shot. This set will become your "go to" resource when you need to add background filler, or mood to your creation.
